points.quoteText: This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.

points.title: You can opt out of promotional communications
points.quoteText:
This information is used to contact you about the products/services on our site in which you have expressed interest.
At your option, you may also provide demographic information (such as gender or age) about yourself, but it is not required.

points.title: This service uses third-party cookies for statistics
points.quoteText: 3.7.2. Medtinker does not  actively pursue  the use of cookies or other tracking software  in order to track the Personal Information of our Users. However certain third party services that we utilize may or may not use cookies in order to improve the technical functionality of the website.

points.quoteText: 1.1. Medtinker (“us”, ”we” or ”our”) operates https://www.medtinker.net (“Site” or “website”). This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the website and any other services belonging to the above mentioned website.

points.title: Third parties may be involved in operating the service
points.quoteText: Certain third party services that we employ may or may not collect and utilize Personal Information without or explicit consent. By using our services you agree to the collection and use of information by third party services in accordance with this policy, the privacy policy of the respective services we employ as well as international and national or locally applicable standards and laws.

points.title: The service provides details about what kinds of personal information they collect
points.quoteText:
Like many site operators, we collect information that your browser sends whenever you visit our website (“Log Data”).

3.1.2. This Log Data may include information such as your computer’s Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, browser type, browser version, the pages of our Site that you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages and other statistics.

3.1.3. If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.

points.title: You maintain ownership of your data
points.quoteText:
3.5.1. You may opt out of any future contacts from us at any time. You can do the following at any time by contacting us via the email address or contact form given on our website:

  • See what data we have about you, if any.
  • Change/correct any data we have about you.
  • Have us delete any data we have about you.
  • Express any concern you have about our use of your data.

points.title: You have the right to leave this service at any time
points.quoteText: 3.5.2. As well as the above mentioned methods, you may modify the publicly available data that is stored on our website using the profile function available to your account.
